{"id":1637,"date":"2024-08-16T21:01:45","date_gmt":"2024-08-16T21:01:45","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1637"},"modified":"2024-08-16T21:01:45","modified_gmt":"2024-08-16T21:01:45","slug":"mission-061","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-061\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #061: The Black Emboar"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Mission #061: The Black Emboar<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Crater Town, southwest house &#8211; man inside<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Completed main story missions up until Crater Town<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Help a man in Crater Town find his brother in the KBT Expressway<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td><u>Item<\/u>: <strong>TM98 Work Up, Motorcycle<\/strong><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>A man asks you to go find his brother in the KBT Expressway. It\u2019s infested with a gang known as the Black Emboar, and once you get them to leave your reward will be TM98 Work Up and a Motorcycle.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-southwest-house.jpg\" alt=\"The southwest house \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The southwest house<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Enter the southwest house in Crater Town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/02-pokemon-unbound-mission-accepted.jpg\" alt=\"Mission accepted \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Mission accepted<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The man who lives here has a brother who has been kidnapped by a ruthless gang called the Black Emboar, and they\u2019ve gone to the KBT Expressway.<\/p>\n<p>The KBT Expressway can be accessed from the northern exit of Crater Town.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/17-pokemon-unbound-the-entrance-to-the-kbt-expressway.jpg\" alt=\"The entrance to the KBT Expressway \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The entrance to the KBT Expressway<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/03-pokemon-unbound-the-expressway.jpg\" alt=\"The Expressway \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Expressway<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Expressway is a massive tunnel system that connects most towns in Borrius, though only a few parts are open to you at the moment.<\/p>\n<p>This section is crawling with biker thugs that call themselves the Black Emboar, and you\u2019ll have to fight through a bunch of them one by one to proceed.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center even-2col tbl-125img\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Trainers<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><strong>Black Emboar Goon A<\/strong><\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Tepig<\/strong><br \/>\n        Fire<br \/>\n        (Lv.19)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/04-pokemon-unbound-tepig.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Grimer<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/05-pokemon-unbound-grimer.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Koffing<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/06-pokemon-unbound-koffing.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><strong>Black Emboar Goon B<\/strong><\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Tepig<\/strong><br \/>\n        Fire<br \/>\n        (Lv.19)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/04-pokemon-unbound-tepig.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Salandit<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison\/Fire<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/07-pokemon-unbound-salandit.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><strong>Black Emboar Goon C<\/strong><\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Numel<\/strong><br \/>\n        Fire\/Ground<br \/>\n        (Lv.19)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/08-pokemon-unbound-numel.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Koffing<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/06-pokemon-unbound-koffing.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><strong>Black Emboar Goon D<\/strong><\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Ekans<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/09-pokemon-unbound-ekans.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Koffing<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.21)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/06-pokemon-unbound-koffing.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Tepig<\/strong><br \/>\n        Fire<br \/>\n        (Lv.19)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/04-pokemon-unbound-tepig.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Trubbish<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/10-pokemon-unbound-trubbish.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Numel<\/strong><br \/>\n        Fire\/Ground<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/08-pokemon-unbound-numel.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>There are four of them, and they are all along the path that heads north.<\/p>\n<p>So you\u2019d follow that along to continue.<\/p>\n<h3>Black Emboar Boss &#8211; James<\/h3>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/11-pokemon-unbound-james-is-big-brawny-and-the-boss.jpg\" alt=\"James is big, brawny, and the Boss \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>James is big, brawny, and the Boss<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Eventually you\u2019ll come to an intersection and the object of your mission.<\/p>\n<p>Speak to the big man here and he\u2019ll reveal himself as James, the boss of the Black Emboar. He\u2019ll immediately challenge you to a battle to test your worth.<\/p>\n<table class=\"table grey center even-2col tbl-125img\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"class=\"text-large center\">Black Emboar Boss James<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td colspan=\"2\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/12-pokemon-unbound-black-emboar-boss-james.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Koffing<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison<br \/>\n        (Lv.20)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/06-pokemon-unbound-koffing.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Salandit<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison\/Fire<br \/>\n        (Lv.21)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/07-pokemon-unbound-salandit.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Alolan Grimer<\/strong><br \/>\n        Poison\/Dark<br \/>\n        (Lv.22)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/13-pokemon-unbound-alolan-grimer.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Pignite<\/strong><br \/>\n        Fire\/Fighting<br \/>\n        (Lv.22)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/14-pokemon-unbound-pignite.png\" alt=\"\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>When you beat him, he\u2019ll be so impressed that he\u2019ll name the gang after you. <\/p>\n<p>When you ask him about your mission, he\u2019ll tell you that he\u2019s actually the brother the man is looking for!<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/15-pokemon-unbound-james-is-actually-the-missing-brother.jpg\" alt=\"James is actually the missing brother \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>James is actually the missing brother<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You go back to Crater Town together to confront his brother, who was just worried he was getting himself into too much trouble.<\/p>\n<p>James says that his gang is off to Antisis City to take up residence there, and has a parting gift for you.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/061\/16-pokemon-unbound-the-motorcycle-is-the-same-as-the-bicycle-from-other-games.jpg\" alt=\"The Motorcycle is the same as the Bicycle from other games \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Motorcycle is the same as the Bicycle from other games<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll get your very own Motorcycle, which you can assign to the Select button from the Cube menu. Not only will it be much faster than the Running Shoes, but wild Pok\u00e9mon encounters are reduced while riding it.<\/p>\n<p>He\u2019ll also give you TM98 Work Up.<\/p>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1638,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1637","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1637","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":tru